text: Mary Cynthia Walsh (born May 13, 1952) is a Canadian actress, comedian, and writer."Mary Walsh". The Canadian Encyclopedia, January 1, 2012. She was born in St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador, Canada. She is known for her role in This Hour Has 22 Minutes. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:Canadian comedians Category:Living people
